          <li><strong>One-handed height adjustment</strong> — easy to switch positions</li>
          <li><strong>Removable keyboard tray included</strong> — ergonomic typing position</li>
          <li><strong>No assembly required, ready in 5 minutes</strong> — out of box ready</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=standing+desk+converter&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it wins at this price</h3>
      <p>Most standing desk converters either wobble or have limited height range. The FlexiSpot uses a gas spring mechanism that's both stable and easy to adjust. The 28-inch surface comfortably fits two monitors, making it ideal for multitaskers.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Office workers who want to alternate between sitting and standing throughout the day. It's perfect for those who can't replace their existing desk but want the health benefits of standing work.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
